tracks.description: A FRHD Contest Entry. Wow, it's satisfying to finally publish it... I just can't finish it in time, though. Anyway, enjoy it, I made sure it's not too easy ;)

Explore an city left to rot due to some deadly sun flares a while back and WICKED's desperation to find a cure. Based on the second book in the Maze Runner Series. RC9R1.

So since the first 2 remakes of my old tracks went so well i decided to remake one of my biggest trials. it's not too hard so most people should be able to beat it. once i hit 200 subs I'll take a break to work on a 200 sub special for a couple months. or I'll do collabs. whichever i feel like.

Some inspiration from Plasticorp 4 by Ness, and here's what I got for my entry for pssst's Remix Contest 4 Round 3. 30 minutes for ghosting this isn't a problem, even though I broke the keyboard. For the first time I actually feel proud of myself doing a map :D And also... bye pssst :(
